Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的能飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼飛得起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,從頭到尾都是Hello, Happy的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要知道自己無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,香澄她們就能找回笑容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太佩服心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,暈船了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像…突然失去了緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,薰！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一臉悲傷 我的小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有化作一隻飛鳥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看到你後背長出了純白的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如夢似幻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 睜開眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,薰！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是這樣
Comment: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,EDJP P
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是Hello, Happy World！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,米歇爾 米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,美咲 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人睡著都是笑容呢 太好了
